name: Random Numbers 002 - Black and White
description:
Using Excel to create random number art. This piece reminds me of television snow from when I was younger (very pre-streaming). It is that space in-between channels; before you find what you were looking for, but after you reject something else.

The piece morphs through 3 unique random number screens. They are entirely unique and impossible to repeat. Created in excel using a random number generator and then colour-coded according to a set distribution: 

White: ~1%, 
Light Grey: ~80%,
Dark Grey: ~13%, 
Black: ~6%

This is the second in a series of "Random Number Generated Art". Ping me on Twitter if you liked it.
